{"article_id":"2Tz6bMBkn2kCGLej","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump 's plan","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to deter school shootings","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"does not include his repeated calls","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"to raise the age","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"for buying semi-automatic rifles","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to 21 .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"But he is moving ahead with his controversial proposal","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"to provide firearms training to school employees .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"The president tweeted","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that there was not much political support","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"for raising the minimum age on weapons sales .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Americans must be 18","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to buy a rifle or shotgun","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and 21","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to buy a handgun from licensed dealers under federal law .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Private , unlicensed sales are federally allowed at any age for rifles and shotguns , and 18 for handguns ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"according to the Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms and Explosives .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"The White House unveiled its proposals on Sunday night ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"following an attack at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that left 17 dead in Parkland , Florida , on 14 February .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The 19-year-old suspect","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who allegedly used a legally purchased semi-automatic rifle","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"to attack Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School -","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"is charged with 17 counts of murder .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"White House officials described Sunday 's plan as a fulfilment of the president 's call for action after Parkland .","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"Encourage military veterans and retired police officers to become teachers","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"The White House said","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"a new federal commission on school safety would examine the age limit issue .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Mr Trump tweeted on Monday :","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"`` On 18 to 21 Age Limits ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"watching court cases and rulings","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"before acting . `","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"` States are making this decision .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Things are moving rapidly on this ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"but not much political support","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"( to put it mildly ) . ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Education Secretary Betsy DeVos ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"who will chair the new federal commission on school safety ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the proposals were `` meaningful actions , steps","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that can be taken right away","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to help protect students '' .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Speaking last month ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"the Republican president had suggested","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"it was a problem","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that Americans can legally buy semi-automatic rifles from the age of 18 ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"yet have to wait until 21","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"to buy handguns .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"`` I mean ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"so they buy a revolver","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"- a handgun -","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"they buy at the age of 21 , ''","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"he told school officials .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"`` And yet , these other weapons","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"that we talk about ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"they 're allowed to buy them at 18 . `","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"` So how does that make sense ?","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"We 're going to work on getting the age up to 21 instead of 18 . ''","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"He had also accused members of his own party of being `` petrified '' of the National Rifle Association","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"( NRA ) .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The Republican president said","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"the NRA has `` great power over you people '' ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"but `` less power over me '' .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"However , Mr Trump himself came under pressure from the country 's top gun lobby not to change existing legislation .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Following his repeated calls","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"to raise the age limit ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"a representative for the gun lobby visited the White House earlier this month .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Afterwards , chief NRA lobbyist Chris Cox tweeted","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"he had a `` great meeting '' ,","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"and the president and vice-president `` do n't want gun control '' .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"The NRA is suing Florida","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"after it passed a gun control law","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"which raises the legal age","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"for buying rifles","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"to 21 .","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"The lobby argues","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"the bill violates the US constitution .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Chuck Schumer , leader of the opposition Democrats in the Senate , tweeted","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that the White House 's action plan amounts to `` baby steps '' .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Avery Gardiner , co-president of the Brady Campaign","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"to Prevent Gun Violence , said :","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"`` Americans","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"expecting real leadership","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"to prevent gun violence","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"will be disappointed and troubled by President Trump 's dangerous retreat from his promise . ''","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Survivors of the Florida shooting have been pressing for a complete ban on sales of assault-style rifles to the public .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":173,"left":172,"right":86,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":103,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":94,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":92,"right":93,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":92,"left":88,"right":91,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":2,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":89,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":89,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":96,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":8,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":99,"right":100,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":97,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":111,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":110,"right":25,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":105,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":17,"right":104,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":24,"relation":"same-unit","nucl